  <description>
    <p>
      Null IDE is a professional-grade code editor and security toolkit designed for 
      ethical hackers, security researchers, and developers. It combines the power of 
      Monaco Editor with over 60 integrated security testing tools.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Monaco Code Editor with syntax highlighting for 50+ languages</li>
      <li>Built-in terminal with PTY support (node-pty)</li>
      <li>SQL Injection Scanner (SQLi, Blind SQLi, Time-based)</li>
      <li>XSS Scanner (Reflected, Stored, DOM-based)</li>
      <li>JWT Token Analyzer and Decoder</li>
      <li>GraphQL Security Scanner</li>
      <li>LDAP &amp; XPath Injection Testing</li>
      <li>NoSQL Injection Scanner</li>
      <li>Race Condition Detector</li>
      <li>Cache Poisoning Testing</li>
      <li>DNS Rebinding Attack Tool</li>
      <li>API Rate Limit Testing</li>
      <li>Request Interceptor &amp; Repeater</li>
      <li>Encoding/Decoding Tools (Base64, URL, Hex, etc.)</li>
      <li>Hash Generator (MD5, SHA1, SHA256, SHA512)</li>
      <li>Network Tools (Port Scanner, DNS Lookup, WHOIS)</li>
      <li>Serial/USB Device Monitor</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      All tools operate locally with no external data transmission, ensuring 
      complete privacy for your security research.
    </p>
  </description>
